flowchart TD
  %% Roles
  subgraph Roles
    U[User (Finder)]
    FM[Finder Dept Manager]
    QC[QC Manager]
    ASME[NCR Coordinator / ASME]
    RM[Receiver Dept Manager]
    PICNCR[PIC of CA (NCR)]
    PICCAPA[PIC of CAPA]
  end

  %% NCR Flow
  U -->|Create NCR| NCR_Draft[Status: Draft]
  NCR_Draft -->|Submit| NCR_PFA[Status: Pending_Finder_Approval]

  FM -->|Approve + comment| NCR_PQR[Status: Pending_QC_Registration]
  FM -->|Reject + reason| NCR_Draft

  QC -->|QC Registration| NCR_PAR[Status: Pending_ASME_Review]
  QC -->|Reject/Return (optional)| NCR_Draft

  ASME -->|ASME Review| NCR_STR[Status: Sent_To_Receiver]

  %% Receiver handling
  RM -->|Assign PIC of CA + Disposition| NCR_ASSIGNED[Status: Sent_To_Receiver (PIC assigned)]
  NCR_STR --> NCR_ASSIGNED

  %% Decision: CAPA needed?
  NCR_ASSIGNED -->|Disposition requires CAPA| CAPA_CREATE[Create CAPA (from NCR)]
  NCR_ASSIGNED -->|Disposition no CAPA| NCR_CLOSE_READY[Ready to Close]

  %% CAPA flow
  CAPA_CREATE -->|Assign PIC CAPA + Target date| CAPA_IP[CAPA Status: In_Progress]
  PICCAPA -->|Update progress 0-100%| CAPA_IP
  CAPA_IP -->|Progress 100%| CAPA_PV[CAPA Status: Pending_Verification]
  QC -->|Verify effectiveness| CAPA_VER[CAPA Status: Verified]
  CAPA_VER -->|Close CAPA| CAPA_CLOSED[CAPA Status: Closed]

  %% NCR close
  CAPA_CLOSED --> NCR_CLOSE_READY
  NCR_CLOSE_READY -->|Close NCR| NCR_CLOSED[Status: Closed]

